high_descs: Turn right and start walking across the room, then turn left and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the large metal spoon with a black handle off of the counter.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn right and walk over to the sink.
Place the large metal spoon in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and take out the now clean large metal spoon.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn right again and walk over to the large wooden table.
Place the large clean metal spoon on the wooden table standing up behind the small metal spoon closest to you.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean large metal spoon on the wooden table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter just past the sink.
Pick up the ladle from the counter.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Wash the ladle off in the sink.
Turn around and walk to the table in the corner on the opposite side of the room.
Set the ladle down on the table behind the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean ladle on the table in the corner.

high_descs: Walk to your left, then turn right to face the cabinet between the stove and the sink.
Pick up the ladle from the counter top.
Put the ladle in the sink, rinse it off, and pick it back up.
Turn around and walk to the wooden table.
Put the ladle on the table next to the bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean ladle on the wooden table.
